{"tid":995233,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【𢱑晒頭？車頭被攝奇怪利是　車主紛紛稱收過】","createTime":"2019-01-25T09:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T17:27:51.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3c8492ecad207b80b6be095ceb236cfd90094b27","tid":995233,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:41:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>𢱑晒頭？車頭被攝奇怪利是　車主紛紛稱收過</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/bkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fbkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001.html&d=Ev%2FgGGd3hbiNhm%2BUCJXp8AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=affa580b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/bkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/photo/bkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190125172127\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190125172127&h=e5010aa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邊個話香港係文化沙漠？<br />\n<br />\n收到利是是開心事，惟近日元朗有車主在私家車車頭發現一封內含《詩經》節錄的利是封，令人摸不着頭腦。<br />\n<br />\n照片於周四（24日）上載至Facebook群組「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」，只見私家車水撥夾着一封紅色長方形利是封。車主大感困惑：「打開睇，有張完全唔知做乜嘅紙」，紙張上是以簡體字印刷的《關雎》，寫有：「關關雎鳩，在河之洲。窈窕淑女，君子好逑&hellip;」而兩旁則莫名其妙地印有不同人的頭像。<br />\n<br />\n貼文一出，有網友非常錯愕，表示其中一個頭像是自己：「佢用咗我本人張相&hellip;」令事件更添撲朔迷離。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民留言指曾遇到同類事情：「我尋日都收到」、「九龍城都有」，有人開玩笑說：「降頭嚟。師兄，建議你搵個高人睇睇穩陣」。"},{"pid":"847332e33aea7656e5804b58b54551da55c32e94","tid":995233,"uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/photo/bkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190125172127\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190125172127&h=bd1fa38a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車頭竟然被攝了一個利是封？（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/photo/bkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190125172127\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190125172127&h=3c3ac6ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利是封內是一篇《關雎》，令人一頭霧水&hellip;（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/photo/bkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001_04b.jpg?20190125172127\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20190125172127&h=e1c6a47f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網友表示也曾收過離奇利是，裏面還有一張觀音卡。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/photo/bkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001_05p.jpg?20190125172127\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20190125172127&h=8c0794fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九龍城亦曾出現。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/photo/bkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001_06p.jpg?20190125172127\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190125154617987-0125_00822_001_06p.jpg%3F20190125172127&h=d4193dd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網友表示曾在收到利是後懵然不知，還把利是駛到目的地，下車後才發覺。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"c39161834a5ddd26a2a098bdf95bcfbc39910310","tid":995233,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"3c8492ecad207b80b6be095ceb236cfd90094b27","tid":995233,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:41:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>𢱑晒頭？車頭被攝奇怪利是　車主紛紛稱收過</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/bkn-201901